[div class=p 
	"Beat Hellbat ASAP to get his Ex-Skill (SaberSmash), it becomes realy usefull because it does 8 more damage (12 if its effective) after Zero uses his Triple Slash on Bosses/Mid-Bosses. And also get one elemental chip (Electricity Chip) in the second boss.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" In the Second Set of Bosses:
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"Beat Hanumachine ASAP to get his Ex-Skill (SplitHeavens), it is another attack that does 7  more damage (10 if effective) after Triple Combo and can be used before SaberSmash.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Bear Blizzack after Hanumachine to get his Ex-Skill (Blizzard Arrow), it becomes usefull on getting some disks and can be used to finish Anubis faster.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" In the Third Set of Bosses:
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"Beat Glacier ASAP to get his Ex-Skill (OrbitShield), it does 6 more damage (9 if effective) at the beginning of any combo, becoming realy usefull, and it looks awesome.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Beat Foxtar after Gaclier to get a Double Jump Boots, that is realy usefull afterwards.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Beat Kelverian after Foxtar to get his Ex-Skill (GaleAttack), it is insanely usefull, it connects 3 hits (if Charged Slash is not used, otherwise, it'2) and does 6 damage per hit and it can be used after OrbitShield and before SplitHeavens.
	$LF
]div
